text: The Secret of Bacchus () is a 1984 Romanian comedy movie directed by Geo Saizescu and starring Cristina Stamate, Emil Hossu, Ștefan Mihăilescu-Brăila, Dem Rădulescu, Gheorghe Dinică, Sebastian Papaiani, Jean Constantin, Octavian Cotescu. ==Other websites== * Category:1984 comedy movies Category:Romanian comedy movies
title: The Secret of Bacchus
